data.description:
Immaculate move-in ready home in quiet, gated community in a cul-de-sac. This home is extremely well maintained, gorgeous laminate floors throughout the home, large loft with nook and extra cabinet space. 
Kitchen with island, pantry, recessed lighting, all appliances are included.
Primary bedroom with two closets, bathroom with upgraded floors, double sinks, large tub and separate shower.
Large private backyard with gate and gazebo. Very conveniently located within minutes from freeway, shopping mall, restaurants, casinos and hospital.
